{
  "texts": [
    "External validation is therefore a pivotal pre-deployment step.",
    "Some studies in this review reported improvement in performance on external test sets when self-supervised pretraining was conducted [43,64,179], but further work is required to confidently characterize this phenomenon.",
    "LimitationsDespite the comprehensiveness of this survey, some limitations must be noted.",
    "First, the study's exclusive focus on self-supervision excluded adjacent categories of machine learning used in practice to produce feature extractors for transfer learning.",
    "Supervised pretraining on datasets of medical images can also produce feature extractors [187]."
  ]
}